Roba poppenwieg

Roba dolls cradle

Put your dolls to rest in this white lacquered Roba Fienchen dolls cradle. This sweet cradle comes with a curtain, blanket and pillow. The materials are tested for harmful substances and found to be child friendly. The material can be easily cleaned.
